track_notes: This is a very beautifull path to the summit that you do in winter. The road is closed until last april/may and the snowshoes are welcome. You will found a castle at the summit and a very nice panorama.

Conditions are not very good, few snow and much ice! So i used the road to go and the snowshoes for the return. Very cold on summit -3c and Wind.
Much pleasant in summertime
track_title: Using the road because much ice

track_notes: This place is fine also in winter time! You must park at the ski resort named Camp dArgent, then walk with snow-shoes until the guard house, after you can walk up the crest; the slope is dangerous, so take care. Plenty room on summit for antenna

You can walk to this summit in 5 minutes time!
Start from the summer park car.
do not show the guards your antenna!!!!
Dpart depuis le parking Camp dArgent. Niveau facile.
